|---|---|---|
| **Extension Popup** | Extension popup window | Quick actions: trigger autofill, view status, see matched fields |
| **Options Page** | Dedicated browser tab | Full master profile editor, resume upload, settings, field history |
| **Content Script** | Every matched web page | Scrape form fields (labels, types, options), inject values, trigger DOM events |
| **Background Script** | Extension service worker | Central hub: routes messages, calls backend API, manages `chrome.storage` |
| **Backend API** | Your server (or cloud) | Receives form fields + user profile → calls AI → returns mapped values |
| **Gemini AI** | Google Cloud | Semantic field matching, answer generation for open-ended questions |

