## 4. Data Flow

### 4.1 Complete Autofill Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant P as 🖱️ Popup UI
    participant CS as 📄 Content Script
    participant BG as 🔧 Background Script
    participant API as 🖥️ Backend API
    participant AI as 🤖 Gemini AI

    U->>P: Clicks "AutoFill This Page"
    P->>BG: chrome.runtime.sendMessage({action: "START_AUTOFILL"})
    BG->>CS: chrome.tabs.sendMessage({action: "SCRAPE_FIELDS"})

    Note over CS: Scans DOM for all<br/>input, select, textarea,<br/>radio, checkbox elements

    CS->>BG: Returns FormField[] array
    
    Note over BG: Reads user profile from<br/>chrome.storage.local

    BG->>API: POST /api/match-fields<br/>{profile, fields}
    API->>AI: Construct prompt with<br/>profile + field labels
    AI->>API: Returns matched JSON
    API->>BG: Returns FieldMapping[]

    Note over BG: Separates matched<br/>vs unmatched fields

    BG->>CS: {matched: [...], unmatched: [...]}

    Note over CS: Fills matched fields,<br/>triggers input/change events

    CS->>BG: Reports fill results
    BG->>P: Updates UI with status

    alt Has Unmatched Fields
        P->>U: Shows unmatched fields dialog
        U->>P: Provides answers
        P->>BG: Sends user answers
        BG->>CS: Fills remaining fields
    end
```

